  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.PkYYoSwGjKt9BiTo]{Weapon Group: Melee Weapons}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">This unique item is equipped with more than a halfdozen resonant transformers that conduct severe electrical shocks to a target when you impact with a physical hit.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">If you don't hit any creature during a round, at the start of your next turn, increase the damage of your next hit with this weapon by +2. This is cumulative up to +8 damage. After you hit any creature, the bonus is reduced back to 0. At the start of combat, unless you are surprised, the glove is assumed to be primed to +8 damage.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Tesla glove </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 42px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1,500 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 67px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Special lightning </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 32px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">3 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 177px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">AP, augment, finesse, light, pincher, reload (Special-M), TL2</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.iK2nOll8s5dIVgVp]{AP (Armor Piercing)}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.ydcXGCVTDa4gQn8f]{Augment}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.qB35DS5654aWtgir]{Finesse}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.bY9owuVfWrNWp8NV]{Light}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.nEUBgd3Yxs3OUtvD]{Pincher}</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.QjoW3JNAsq3eJt4s]{Reload}</p>",
